entries.femaleVariant: ...And that's why I say fuck him sideways. Hang on, gotta take this.
No fuckin' way.
No damn way…
I'm only going to say this once. I'm in no mood for pranks, so if you don't--
How can I help you?
Hey there, Vik.
V...? Is it really you?
Sure is.
Wrote me off, huh?
Good to hear you.
The one and only.
What, write me off that fast?
You don't know how good it is to hear you.
Unbelievable...
Gotta admit, I knocked back a glass or two over your symbolic grave.
It's good to hear you too, V.
But how're you...? Why?
On my way to see you soon.
Haven't changed a bit, Vik.
Least I can count on you.
Ugh, least I can still count on you bein' there for me.
Huh. Whaddaya mean?
Eh, already holoed someone. Seems not all my relationships stood the test of time.
People move on, V. But, well... sometimes some of 'em come back.
Be on my way to see you soon. Usual spot?
Yeah... in a manner of speaking.
I'll see you, V. You know the address.
Someone grindin' your gears again?
Holy fuck, V?! Or is it Johnny?!
V, V, it's me, The one and only.
Fuck me! Can't believe it, goddam preem you're alive, choom!
Kinda figured you might be happy.
Hey, Jude.
V. Where you been, choom?
At an NUS clinic.
Dunno that I can say.
On the Moon.
NUS clinic. Had surgery. It's a long story.
Must've been a long operation, too. Gruesome, bloody.
Wow, V... thought I'd never see you again.
Dunno that I can talk about it. Classified info, that sorta thing.
Wow... gotta be the worst excuse I've ever heard.
Moon colony. Secret mission for the NUS government.
Pff, right.
No excuse, pure truth.
Spent most of the time in a coma. Unplanned, obviously.
OK, OK, kidding. Well, sorta.
Experiencin' some downsides…
Found a way to excise the biochip.
Should be dead, I know. Good news is, finally found a way to excise the biochip.
What, how? Tellin' me Silverhand's out? You're gonna remain, uh, yourself?
Forever and ever. A hundred percent V.
V, that is beyond nova.
River, it's me.
Me who?
V of course.
Weird question.
Well, uh... V, obviously.
Is it obvious?
How do I know I'm not speakin' to Silverhand?
Stop futzin' around.
The V I knew wouldn'ta waited two years to return a call.
Wow, uh, wasn't expectin' that.
Yeah, well, old cops carry suspicion in their back pocket.
Sorry. Didn't know I'd disappear.
Maybe a "glad you're still alive?"
Dunno, maybe somethin' like "Wow, glad you're not dead?"
Ehh, shit, V, I'm sorry. 'Course I'm happy. Just thought... thought you were gone for good.
Ehh, you're right, sorry. Really am glad you've come up for air.
I was in a coma.
Sorry. Woulda let you know if I'd known I'd be gone that long.
OK, I understand. An accident, anomaly, shouldn't blame you for it.
Been a little touchy lately. Sorry.
If that's what you want...
You outta your mind?
Well, if that's what you want...
It's not. But I just can't.
Goodbye, River.
Bye, V. Thanks for bein' a good presence in my life for a time.
What, why? 'Cause your pride took a hit? You gonked?
Listen... I let myself down.
And bein' a martyr's gonna make it better?
It's just easier for me this way.
Uh, your AV's not quite ready.
Of course. An AV is ready and waiting.
V, V, V…
Won't hear from Johnny anymore.
Won't be hearin' from Johnny anymore, ever.
Y'mean he... he's…?
Yeah.
Shit.
Weird losin' someone a second time like that…
Sorry 'bout that, Kerry.
Yeah, well... still fuckin' glad you're around, yeah?
Hacienda o' yours still standin'?
How's things, Kerry? Hacienda o' yours still standin'?
Who cares 'bout a house? Someplace waaaaay preemer right now.
OK, spill. Somethin's up.
Sittin' on the Crystal Palace as we speak. Played a gig yesterday, had a beaut fuckin' view of Europe. Shit, V, wish you were here.
Yeah, uh, not really in a partyin' mood right now.
How's the career? You recordin', performin'?
Think about me at all?
What about you, Ker, what's up? Career goin' strong?
Actually, fuck yeah! Thanks for askin'!

entries.maleVariant: V, bet your ass I did and do. But man, looked like you were gone for good. Fuckin' hell of a time for me.
Wish you were here now. Sittin' pretty on the Crystal Palace. Played a gig yesterday, had a beaut fuckin' view of Europe.
Yeah, uh, aimin' for cozier landings right now.

entries.femaleVariant: Woke up from a coma.
Well, just woke up from a two-year coma.
Jeez, shit, can you not, choom? 'M on a call, 's that not clear?
Yeah, Ker? D'ya hear what--?
Fuck, yeah, yeah. D'you say coma?
Fuck, V ... Damn, I'm sorry, sounds like shit. You need anything? Eddies maybe or...?
Really wanna talk face to face.
Whoa, sounds serious.
Think we can we meet up?
Ugh, can't now, I'm on tour, will be a while. But if the holo's enough, I'm all yours.
Yeah, got surgery, 's why I'm alive. But... didn't work out, not completely.
Better talk in person.
Need a friend.
Eddies? Really?
Lookin' like everybody needs Kerry, wants a piece o' you…
Yeah, crap coincidence, you know, lots goin' on. Shit luck.
Yeah, shit luck.
Need you.
First thing that comes to mind? Eddies?
Y'know, for meds, treatment, whatever…
Can't treat it, Kerry. Gonna have to live with it till I die.
Ker-- you hear me? Was sayin'...
Hey, hey, chill. I wanna help, OK?
Need a friend, Ker. Really rather not be alone right now.
Kerry?
V, y'know I'd love to help, really would. But I just can't swing it. Playin' Paris tomorrow, then Kyiv…

entries.maleVariant: Wanna know that even though the whole fuckin' world's changed, you're still here for me.
Fuck, V... if I could, I'd be flyin' your way already. But I got gigs, Paris tomorrow, then Kyiv…
I didn't... How could I have known you'd be back at all, or right now? Y'know?

entries.femaleVariant: If not for the tour, I'd be flyin' your way already.
Will I see you again?
Man, are you in fuckin' demand…
Whaddaya think, gonna see you again?
Shit, 'course you will! Listen, soon as I'm back, c'mon over. We'll go wherever you want.
Gimme a couple of months. Or, OK, four tops. Deal?
Sure, deal.
Listen V, in the middle of somethin', kinda. Gotta go, they're callin' me back on stage.
But yeah, you wanna shoot the shit later, hit me up on the holo.
Why don't I believe you?
Wanna help, huh? Why don't I believe you?
Well, kinda odd question, huh?
No, I just... Know you wanna help. But you'll have interviews after the tour, recordings after the interviews…
Ker, hand on heart – am I still part of your life?
So damn nice to know some stories actually get a happy ending.
Dealin; with some drawbacks…
I... I'll never fully recover. I'm alive, sure, but got no idea what comes next.
Shit, you serious?
Really sorry, V. Hope you figure it out, get yourself set up again.
Mind if I come see you?
Thought I could drop by, see you. We'd grab a pizza, talk…
Y'know, a lot's changed...
Preem, fresh NC gossip. Can't wait to hear it.
V, I'm in Pittsburgh. An' I'm married.
If you ever hop to the other coast, c'mon over for a beer, but now? Really can't help you.
Sounds like you don't wanna be a part of it.
Sounds like you're anglin' not be a part of it.
Mad at me for disappearin', right?
No. I mean, sure, I  was, but... finally decided you'da pinged me if you could. Now, it's just…
With you, I will.
'Course I'll make it – got you on my side.
Was afraid you'd say somethin' like that.
What...?
V, listen... a lot's changed. I'm in Pittsburgh, for one.
Hah, finally ditched NC! No worries, I'll just fly over to you.
No, not "to me," "to us." Got married.
Congrats!
Didn't expect that...
Seriously? Congrats, Judy.
Thanks. Wish you coulda come to the wedding.
I'm just glad you found what you were lookin' for.
When you disappeared, I knew I had to get away from Night City. And, well, that's how I met Bianca.
And whaddaya know – I'm happy, V.
Wow, missed so much...
Shit, missed so much...
Y'know, if you hadn't vanished, dunno that I'd ever've left NC. Or met Bianca.
Maybe I should've ghosted sooner.
C'mon, you know it's not like that.
Goodbye, Judy.
That's not... Wasn't expectin' that.
How could you?
Jude – how could you?
Two years, V. I was lonely, lost in my head. First Evelyn, then you... No way I woulda made it alone.
What's her name?
We could've made it.
What's her name?
Bianca. But looks, character – nothin' like you at all.
I'll miss you.
Y'know, we could've made it.
Sure, maybe. But you were dyin', and you up and disappeared. What was I supposed to do?
Gonna miss you.
Yeah.
But I'm good now, V. Please don't take that away.
Don't have much of a choice, do I?
Goodbye, V. And I'm sorry.
Go back to your fairy tale.
Well... bye, Judy. Really hope our paths cross again someday.
Me too, V. And good luck.
Well, later, Judy. Go on, back to your fairy tale.
V, I'm sorry, really. But I know you got this, you'll manage.
Mhm. 'Course I will.
Thought I skipped town?
D'ya think I flew the coop, ran off for good?
Yeah. That, or that Arasaka got you.
Either way, I was furious. Just didn't know who at.
What'd you expect to hear after all this time?
Gotta admit, I'm a little mad at you.
River, I was in a coma. They just woke me up.
Oh shit, V... Sorry.
Here I am bein' a fuckin' asshole to ya…
Something's wrong.
I'd be pissed, too.
'S all right. Be worried if you didn't care.
You OK? Gettin' this vibe that somethin's wrong.
Honestly? Everything is.
Sold 'em a pile o' police secrets, dirt on whoever they wanted...
Ah, 's all right. Be pissed if I were you, too.
V, it's not just about you. Problem's with me, too.
'S OK, River. Be more worried if you didn't seem to give a shit.
I missed you. Wonderin' if I'da chosen better if you'd been here with me.
River...?
I needed money for Randy's rehab. So I did a deal with Trauma.
What's goin' on?
Sheesh, I'm sorry. Should we meet, talk about it?
Lemme come to you, we'll talk.
Didn't have a choice, sounds like.
Clearly didn't have any other options.
How can you possibly know that?
I know you. Woulda done it differently if you'd had a choice.
I dunno... I'd like to believe that, but...
Fuck, River, now I feel bad... Can we meet? Help each other out?
Too late for that.
What? Rather not see me?
Look, I'm not the man you used to know. Couldn't stand to look you in the eye. Not you, not...
The fuck am I blabbin' for ...? I gotta go.
Wait a sec, River...
Wait.
V, sometimes things just don't work out, and it's nobody's fault.
Fuck, I'm so sorry... Listen, I'll come visit you. You'll tell me everything.
I'd rather you didn't.
Can't be serious.
I'm not the man you used to know. You'd do better just forgettin' about me.
Night City – can I get a flight there?
Bear with us, please, it won't be much longer.
I'll come get you now.
Got caught up with the FIA, their ops.
Well, met this netrunner, then used her.
So… this netrunner I met got me involved in this FIA op. They promised surgery, a cure, using the 'runner's tech, in exchange.
And it worked, but not without complications... a two-year coma for one.
God dammit… that's a chunk of life there.
Yep... I mean, they saved me, new lease on life, but chrome's a no-go for me, now. Even simple muscle boosters.
Is that what they told you...?
Quacks, I bet. They overlooked something, I just know it. Come see me, V.
See, met a netrunnin' genius… Made friends, then gave her up to the NUSA. Traded 'er for surgery using their tech.
Well… I won't judge. You had your reasons, I'm sure.
What's it matter? Karma got me good. Spent two years in a coma.
Think I stand a chance of being normal again, my old self?
Of course you do. I've got new tech, does wonders.
World changes, moves on, but Vik's ever the last reliable resort.
Yeah…
Also, chrome's a no-go for me, can't use it. Even simple muscle boosters.
You have reached – Panam Palmer.
We're sorry, the subscriber is currently outside the service area. Please leave a message or call again later.
Guess who's back in the game.
Been a while, huh?
Sorry, Panam Sorry I ghosted on you.
Hey, heyo, Panam. Guess who's back from a little, uh, involuntary vacay?
But, bad jokes aside… guess you must've wondered where I'd gone.
Panam, hey. Been a while since we saw each other. Lots longer than I thought… or wanted.
Guess you're... away somewhere. Hope it's temporary, a waypoint… not outright nomadic flight.
Panam, hey. Um, can't know how deeply fuckin' sorry I am.
Ah, gotta be rage-level mad… Can't blame you… Disappearin' for two years without so much as a "See ya"?
Think I can soothe that a bit? Gotta tell ya, really didn't want to abandon you, really.
Just came out of a coma, docs brought me out.
I can explain. Just have to meet, really wanna.
So, brass tacks… I had surgery. Docs just brought me out of a coma.
Gonna live, new lease and all… but not on the greatest terms.
I can explain everything, I can. Rather do it face to face, though.
It'd just be great right now, really great… if I could see you.
Guess it comes down to… just not wanting to be alone right now.
Ring me back, OK?
I'll be in touch.
Need you, badly.
You find a moment, ring me back, yeah?
So we'll be in touch. I will.
Need you, Panam. Somethin' awful.
See you. Soon.
What the hell'd I say, Yuki...? Let 'em fuckin' tune, I don't need to hold their hand. Long as it's all harmony.
